description:
&lt;p&gt;Bank Theatre Practitioner – Cardiff and Vale – Bank - £20-£23 Ph&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for bank or locum roles? Do you want to work in an environment where you have the time to dedicate time &amp; care to your patients? Do you want to work for the UKs not for profit healthcare provider? If so, Nuffield Health is looking for a Theatre Practitioner at our Nuffield Health Vale Hospital. Get in touch or apply today! &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With drive, passion and high standards, you might join us from the NHS or a private setting. Either way, you will discover unrivalled scope to work autonomously, making full use of your skills and knowledge and adding value.  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There’s free parking onsite, and you’ll be supported by an experienced and close knit team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Bank Theatre Practitioner / ODP you will;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with leading consultants and other like-minded professionals, who will respect and value what you bring to the close-knit multidisciplinary team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy opportunities to work on a varied caseload using technology, equipment and facilities, which are all state-of-the-art.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise, support and develop junior members of staff.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver high quality care and experiences for patients, which is always clinically effective, evidence based and appropriate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;As part of the wider hospital team you will interact with colleagues on the ward because you understand that continuity in patient care is key.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What are we looking for in a Theatre Practitioner / ODP? You will have;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Qualifications and experience relevant to your registration, including NMC or HCPC.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Post-registration experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills and will be a great team worker. You will also be flexible and motivated.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether you are currently in the NHS or a private setting, we are sure you will find your career with us motivating and rewarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Like all of us at Nuffield Health, you do what you do because you care. Every one of our brilliant people is passionate about making a real difference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal visits are welcomed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Location - Cardiff and Vale&lt;br /&gt;Salary - £20-£23 per hour depending on experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bank Contract&lt;/p&gt;
